---
layout: layout
title: Posts
---

<p>
    <strong>Hi, I'm Peter 👋</strong>
</p>
<p>
    Here, I like to share my thoughts on productivity, technology, personal development, and creativity.
</p>
<h1>Posts</h1>
<ul class="post-list">
    {%- for post in collections.post | reverse -%}
        <li>
            <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | date('dd MMMM yyyy') }}</time>
            <span class="post-title">
                <a href={{ post.url }}>{{ post.data.title }}</a>
            </span>
        </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
</ul>